<p>Only the user ID is provided to Google, but not the information contained in the profile mentioned above, or other personal data. Summary data of the created profile is available to us. We do not add data that can be used for identification to the profile associated with the user ID.</p>
<p>You can opt out of tracking by user ID by sending an email to <a href="mailto:privacy@visce.ru ">privacy@visce.ru </a></p>
<p>You can also opt out of the use of cookies by setting the appropriate settings in your browser. Please note that in this case, some functions of the site may not be available. By using this website, you consent to the processing of your data by Google in the manner described above for the purposes listed in these rules.</p>
<p>More information about cookies can be found on the website <a href="https://www.aboutcookies.org " target="_blank">https://www.aboutcookies.org </a>.</p>
<p>* The displayed prices are valid at the time of the request and are based on contracts for a period of 2 years. Tariffs are subject to change depending on the selected products and services. Prices for office space and coworking are based on per person per month based on the availability of equipment. The Terms and Conditions apply.</p><br>
